data.text:
HOURS:

Monday - Saturday: 10:00 am to 5:00 pm

Sunday: 12:00 pm to 5:00 pm

ADMISSION:

Adults - $20

Seniors (65 and up) and Active Military - $18

Youth (ages 6-17) - $12

Child (5 and under) - FREE

Students w/ valid ID - $12

This includes a self-guided tour of the museum, which includes the Pierce-Arrow limousine and WWI trench exhibit, as well as a guided tour of the Manse/birthplace. For guaranteed entry, we recommend that you arrive 1 hour before each tour time to ensure your space on the tour. Tickets are available on a first-come, first-served basis and are likely to sell out early, especially on weekends.
